Develop the flask rest api based platform for Create, Retrieve, update, delete and predict avg price for buying,
 selling and inquiry.

1) Load the data using the given json under dataset folder
2) Create the endpoint for handling requests for retrieve specific car info, create, update , filters etc..
3) Whatever the new changes made to the dataset should be saved to the json file
4) dataset should only only load once using respective hook
5) Vehicle number should only exposed to the PRIME Customer
7) user can order the car , based on customer type discount rate will be applied
8) customers can sell his/her car based on the car properties, system should auto suggest the price based on specification